import React from 'react';
import { Button, Form } from 'semantic-ui-react';

const ContactForm = () => (
    <Form>
        <Form.Field>
            <label>Name</label>
            <input placeholder='Name' />
        </Form.Field>
        <Form.Field>
            <label>Email</label>
            <input placeholder='Email' />
        </Form.Field>
        <Form.Field>
            <label>Message</label>
            <input placeholder='Message' />
        </Form.Field>
        <Button>Submit</Button>
    </Form>
)

export default ContactForm;
